Hi Richard,

"SEAL-ALL" adhesive is fuel resistant, and can be used to repair gas 
tanks and many other products. I try to keep a tube in my toolbox at 
all times.

http://www.totalmotorcycle.com/reviews/SealAllGlueReview.htm

